WEBVTT

00:01.734 --> 00:04.002
It's like there's a
cord between our hearts.

00:05.165 --> 00:08.007
It's you and me. It's
always been you and me.

00:08.957 --> 00:10.841
We belong to each other,

00:11.226 --> 00:13.459
and I don't ever want to
live in a world without you.

00:16.387 --> 00:17.620
We pulled two bodies

00:17.645 --> 00:19.765
out of Falls Lake a couple days ago.

00:19.790 --> 00:21.556
We're charging you
additionally with the murders

00:21.593 --> 00:23.460
of Jim Blackwell and Audrey Ellis.

00:23.762 --> 00:24.938
Norman is nice...

00:24.963 --> 00:26.696
okay, he's kind, he's a good person...

00:27.098 --> 00:28.998
but he just... he has
another side to him.

00:29.100 --> 00:31.167
You know, I don't... I don't
know what you'd call it,

00:31.269 --> 00:32.969
maybe multiple
personalities or something,

00:33.071 --> 00:34.594
but he... he changes.

00:40.812 --> 00:43.379
I'm coming for you when
you least expect it.

00:48.053 --> 00:49.018
Hello, Norman.

00:49.772 --> 00:50.954
All right. Get him out.

00:51.056 --> 00:52.587
And get in the back.

00:52.958 --> 00:54.290
What do you want with us, Alex?

00:54.392 --> 00:55.916
You're gonna take me to her body.

